      <title>Flutter基础(一)</title>
      <link href="/2019/01/07/flutter/flutter01-flutter-ji-chu-yi/"/>
      <url>/2019/01/07/flutter/flutter01-flutter-ji-chu-yi/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Flutter横跨Android、iOS、MacOS、Windows、Linux等多个系统，还可以打包成Web程序运行在浏览器上。</p><span id="more"></span><h1 id="1-概念"><a href="#1-概念" class="headerlink" title="1 概念"></a>1 概念</h1><ul><li>概念<ul><li>Flutter的核心概念：组件、构建、状态、框架等。</li><li>组件(Widget)<ul><li>指Flutter应用程序用户界面的基本构建块，定义如下。<ul><li>一种动画处理，例如缓动。</li><li>一种布局，例如填充或滚动。</li><li>一个文本样式，例如字体或颜色。</li><li>一个手势处理，GestureDetector。</li><li>一个界面组件，例如按钮或输入框。</li></ul></li><li>通过属性改变组件的状态以及回调方法的处理，通过方法提供了组件的一些功能扩展。</li><li>组件嵌套的组合方式带来的最大好处即解耦，最基础的组件类是Widget，其他皆继承。<ul><li>无状态组件(StatelessWidget)，界面不发生变化，例如Text、AssetImage等。</li><li>有状态组件(StatefulWidget)，界面会发生变化，例如Scrollable、Animatable等。</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><pre class="line-numbers language-dart"><code class="language-dart"><span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">// 组件嵌套：界面中添加一个剧中组件Center</span><span class="token keyword">return</span> <span class="token function">Center</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>  <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">// 居中组件里嵌套一个容器组件Container</span>  child<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token function">Container</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">// 容器组件里嵌套一个装饰器BoxDecoration</span>    decoration<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token function">BoxDecoration</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>    <span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>    <span class="token comment" spellcheck="true">// 容器组件里嵌套一个文本组件Text</span>    child<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token function">Text</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>    <span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>  <span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
